            <br />
            <span class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl"
              >Lifelong Learner</span
            >
            <span class="text-violet-500">.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg max-w-xl mb-6">
            I love building meaningful things with React.js.
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
            <a
              href="#project"
              class="px-6 py-4 rounded-md bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white"
              >Projects</a
            >
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="px-6 py-4 rounded-md text-black flex gap-2"
              >Let's Talk
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width={1.5}
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="w-6 h-6"
              >
                <path
